<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [kjv]&nbsp; And their meat offering shall be of flour mingled with oil, three tenth deals to a bullock, and two tenth deals to one ram, 
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [bbe]&nbsp; And their meal offering, the best meal mixed with oil, three tenth parts for an ox, two tenth parts for a male sheep, 
