<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [kjv]&nbsp; And ye shall offer a burnt offering, a sacrifice made by fire, of a sweet savour unto the LORD; thirteen young bullocks, two rams, and fourteen lambs of the first year; they shall be without blemish: 
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [bbe]&nbsp; And give a burned offering, an offering made by fire of a sweet smell to the Lord, thirteen oxen, two male sheep, fourteen he-lambs of the first year, all without any mark on them; 
