<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [kjv]&nbsp; And their meat offering shall be of flour mingled with oil, three tenth deals unto every bullock of the thirteen bullocks, two tenth deals to each ram of the two rams, 
<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [bbe]&nbsp; And their meal offering, the best meal mixed with oil, three tenth parts for every one of the thirteen oxen, two tenth parts for every male sheep, 
